item.title: Sister Bliss In Session - 12/07/24
item.description: Sister Bliss is one of the true pioneers of modern dance music and the musical force behind multi-million selling ionic British band Faithless. Each week Sister Bliss In Session showcases the worlds best new upfront electronic music, spinning world exclusives, a live DJ mix, A List artists and DJs on the phone, and a run down of the taste-making Cool Cuts Chart...
